{"id": "test-02637", "text": "CRICKET - WOOLMER MAKES SENTIMENTAL RETURN TO KANPUR.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 10, "end": 17, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "WOOLMER"}, {"start": 46, "end": 52, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "KANPUR"}]}
{"id": "test-02638", "text": "KANPUR, India 1996-12-07", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 6, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "KANPUR"}, {"start": 8, "end": 13, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "India"}]}
{"id": "test-02639", "text": "South Africa's trip to Kanpur for the third test against India has given former England test cricketer Bob Woolmer the chance of a sentimental return to his birthplace.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 12, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "South Africa"}, {"start": 23, "end": 29, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Kanpur"}, {"start": 57, "end": 62, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "India"}, {"start": 80, "end": 87, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "England"}, {"start": 103, "end": 114, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bob Woolmer"}]}
{"id": "test-02640", "text": "Woolmer was born in the northern city of Kanpur when his father worked there for an insurance compnay and was himself an active cricketer.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 7, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Woolmer"}, {"start": 41, "end": 47, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Kanpur"}]}
{"id": "test-02641", "text": "\"It's been a sentimental journey ...", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02642", "text": "A visit to India is always an intriguing experience, \"Woolmer, now the South African coach, said on Saturday.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 11, "end": 16, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "India"}, {"start": 54, "end": 61, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Woolmer"}, {"start": 71, "end": 84, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "South African"}]}
{"id": "test-02643", "text": "Woolmer, 48, played 19 tests for England between 1975 and 1981.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 7, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Woolmer"}, {"start": 33, "end": 40, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "England"}]}
{"id": "test-02644", "text": "His first cricketing sojurn to India was as a member of Tony Greig's England side in 1976-77.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 31, "end": 36, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "India"}, {"start": 56, "end": 66, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Tony Greig"}, {"start": 69, "end": 76, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "England"}]}
{"id": "test-02645", "text": "His father Clarence Woolmer represented United Province, now renamed Uttar Pradesh, in India's Ranji Trophy national championship and captained the state during 1949.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 11, "end": 27, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Clarence Woolmer"}, {"start": 40, "end": 55, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "United Province"}, {"start": 69, "end": 82, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Uttar Pradesh"}, {"start": 87, "end": 92, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "India"}, {"start": 95, "end": 107, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Ranji Trophy"}]}
{"id": "test-02646", "text": "Now aged 86, Woolmer senior lives with his son in Cape Town.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 13, "end": 20, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Woolmer"}, {"start": 50, "end": 59, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Cape Town"}]}
{"id": "test-02647", "text": "Woolmer's memories of Kanpur are few and blurred.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 7, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Woolmer"}, {"start": 22, "end": 28, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Kanpur"}]}
{"id": "test-02648", "text": "\"I don't remember much of the place, \"he said. \"", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02649", "text": "I came here on zero and left at three (aged three) when my father was transferred to Calcutta where I spent another four and half years.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 85, "end": 93, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Calcutta"}]}
{"id": "test-02650", "text": "\"But I do remember we had a cobra snake in the basement of our house.", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02651", "text": "Also that my father bought a bicycle and when we rode over a hose pipe it broke into two. \"", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02652", "text": "Woolmer said the hospital where he was born is close to the stadium where the India-South Africa test will be played.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 7, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Woolmer"}, {"start": 78, "end": 96, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "India-South Africa"}]}
